    <p>Dental offices often struggle with <strong>inaccurate inventory tracking</strong>. This leads to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Overstocking</strong> and <strong>wasted expired supplies</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Stockouts</strong> of essential items</li>
      <li><strong>Time wasted</strong> on manual inventory checks</li>
      <li><strong>Lack of visibility</strong> into inventory levels and usage</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These issues impact <strong>efficiency, cost, and even patient care.</strong></p>
  </section>

